trans-unit.source: Enumerates the elements of an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Räknar upp elementen i en <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: To get an IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A> method of an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.
trans-unit.target: För att få en IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract, använder du <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A>metoden <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns the key and the value of the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref> entry.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar nyckeln och värdet för aktuellt <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"> </xref> transaktionen.

trans-unit.source: After an enumerator is created or after the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> method is called, the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before calling the GetEntry method; otherwise, the return value of GetEntry is undefined.
trans-unit.target: När du har skapat en uppräknare eller efter den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>metoden anropas den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>metoden måste anropas för att gå vidare uppräknaren till det första elementet i mängden innan du anropar metoden GetEntry; annars returvärdet för GetEntry är odefinierad.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>

trans-unit.source: GetEntry also throws an exception if the last call to <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: GetEntry också genererar ett undantag om senast anropet till <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>returnerade `false`, vilket anger slutet av samlingen.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: GetEntry does not move the position of the enumerator, and consecutive calls to GetEntry return the same object until either <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: GetEntry inte flytta positionen för uppräknaren och efterföljande anrop till GetEntry returnera samma objekt förrän antingen <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>eller <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>kallas.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>
